App Links allow users to redirect from a web URL/email to the mobile app. If this file is missing or incorrectly configured for the App Link host/domain, a malicious app can hijack such URLs. playstore_details.title: Aetna Better Health - Medicaid
playstore_details.description:
Aetna Better Health is an easy app for Medicaid members of Aetna Better Health to access their health care information and services. 

As an Aetna Better Health Medicaid member, you may use the app to: 
•    Find or change your provider 
•    View your medical and prescription claims 
•    View your current medications
      o    View your benefits
      o    Set up a new account which may be used for both mobile and web
•    Connect with the health plan through your secure inbox to:
      o    Request an ID card
      o    Request a change in PCP
 
One more of your Aetna Better Health benefits - now available as a mobile app!
 
NOTE: Aetna commercial members looking to access their health plan or search for network doctors can find this information by downloading the Aetna Mobile App.
